description:
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be required to work as a skilled member of the Cardiothoracic Critical Care nursing team to assist in the high provision of care to patients and families. This includes assessment planning, implementation and evaluation of care of patients using agreed care pathways. They will develop and maintain good unit management and organisational skills and assist with the provision of an environment conducive to the education of staff. Duties also to include the cleaning, maintenance and safe handling of equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
